summary:
As someone who has spent 20 years working in IT infrastructure, I bring a wealth of experience to the table as a digital transformation strategist. I am passionate about using my knowledge to drive innovation and change across organizations, and my track record in people management, strategy & planning, and large-scale project sponsorship.
I believe in the power of business partnering to understand objectives and deliver cost-effective solutions that drive measurable results. I have honed my ability to lead global, cross-cultural teams, and I take great pride in my ability to relate to varied audiences, driving innovation and change across groups, functions, and geographies.
Ultimately, my combination of leadership, technical expertise, and collaborative approach allows me to deliver cost-effective solutions and drive innovation and change for organizations of all sizes. I'm excited to bring my experience and passion to any team or project that I work with.
